e.org/web/20161225145702/http://www.sinarharian.com.my/eng/bersatu-joins-pakatan-harapan-1.596132|archive-date=2016-12-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nst.com.my/news/2016/12/196556/ppbm-officially-signs-agreement-join-pakatan-harapan |title=PPBM Officially Signs Agreement To Join Pakatan Harapan |format= |work= |accessdate=2016-12-13 |archive-date=2021-01-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126031529/https://www.nst.com.my/news/2016/12/196556/ppbm-officially-signs-agreement-join-pakatan-harapan |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.malaysiakini.com/news/366041 |title=Harapan And Bersatu Formalise Electoral Pact |format= |work= |accessdate=2016-12-13 |archive-date=2019-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503071557/https://www.malaysiakini.com/news/366041 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2016/12/14/pakatan-harapan-forms-pact-wan-azizah-ppbm-cooperation-just-a-first-step-ahead-of-ge14/ |title=Wan Azizah: PPBM Cooperation Just a First Step Ahead of GE14 |work=D. Kanyakumari |accessdate=2017-02-13 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925232236/https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2016/12/14/pakatan-harapan-forms-pact-wan-azizah-ppbm-cooperation-just-a-first-step-ahead-of-ge14/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2017年3月14日，土著团结党终于正式加入希望联盟成为成员党。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mstar.com.my/berita/berita-semasa/2017/03/14/ppbm-setuju/ |title=PPBM Setuju Sertai Pakatan Harapan, Cadang Tukar Nama |format= |work= |accessdate=2017-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170316002959/http://www.mstar.com.my/berita/berita-semasa/2017/03/14/ppbm-setuju/ |archive-date=2017-03-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mynewshub.cc/utama-sensasi/ppbm-sah-setuju-sertai-pakatan-harapan/ |title=PPBM Sah Setuju Sertai Pakatan Harapan |format= |work= |accessdate=2017-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170315155417/ht